string.name: heading3
string.p: Chandigarh,also known as \"City Beautiful\",is pictuesquely located at the foothills of Shivaliks.It is considered as one of the best experiments in urban planning and modern architecture in India.The city has several tourist attractions like Rock Garden,Sukhna Lake,Rose Garden and is in close proximity to several other tourist post like Shimla,Kasauli,Parwanoo,Manali etc.We are also planning a \"Run for the girl child\" at the Sukhna Lake for the delegates along with city residents for rising public awarness about the radiologists".Delegates travelling from oversea can use the opportunity to visit Taj Mahal,Golden Temple and Jaipur.Chandigarh is well connected to major Indian cities by road,air and rail network.In addition,flight connectivity with many more international destinations is envisaged in near future.
